	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The potentially distressing news: <a href="https://blogs.microsoft.com/blog/2018/06/04/microsoft-github-empowering-developers/" class="postlink">Microsoft plans to acquire GitHub</a> for <a href="https://soylentnews.org/article.pl?sid=18/06/04/0045219" class="postlink">7.5 billion USD</a>.<br /><br />The reassuring news: Despite there being more &quot;Satan&quot; in the name under Satya Nadella than under Steve Ballmer, there's been less &quot;Satan&quot; in Microsoft's attitude toward free software. (Windows 10 telemetry potentially being bait for fishing expeditions aside.)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
